ECB’s Knot Tells NRC Greece Has Reduce Wages, Production Costs

-- B y   M a r t i j n   v a n   d e r   S t a r r e
-- 
2011-09-23T05:05:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/ecb-s-knot-tells-nrc-greece-has-reduce-wages-production-costs.html
European Central Bank Governing
Council member Klaas Knot said  Greece  will have to reform its
economy to become competitive with the rest of  Europe  again, NRC
Handelsblad reported today, citing an interview.  They’ll have to lower wages and cut production costs, Knot
was cited as saying by the Dutch newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Martijn van der Starre at 
 vanderstarre@bloomberg.net  